(232, 1, '2005-11-29 22:27:57', '2005-11-29 22:27:57', 'Welcome to the dynastyBlog.  I will be covering Genealogical issues in this blog including genetic genealogy and the development of dynastyDB, a ''Single Name yDNA'' study database application.  I am not averse to discussing history as it relates to both general human development and family history.  I hope to keep this blog quite busy and encourage comments and observations.\r\n\r\nMy discovery of how popular genetic genealogy is getting has re-fired my enthusiaum in continuing to develop dynastyDB which originally did not include the yDNA aspect.  My hope is that with the feedback I hope to get, I will be able to release the application for other research projects.  If you would like to know more about dynastyDB, please visit the <a href="http://dynastydb.mukudu.net/">Home Page</a>.\r\n\r\nCheers', 'Welcome 2 dynastyBlog', 0, '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2-revision', '', '', '2005-11-29 22:27:57', '2005-11-29 22:27:57', '', 2, 'http://www.dynastyblog.net/2005/11/29/232/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
