(159, 3, '2007-08-23 00:04:00', '2007-08-22 23:04:00', 'In response to DNA analyst''s requests for more sensitive quantitation, Promega announces the release of the Plexor HY System. Plexor HY provides ultra-sensitive quantitation results down to 6.4pg of autosomal or Y-chromosomal DNA. The degree of sensitivity, along with the inclusion of an internal positive control and unique melt curve analysis - guards against false negative and false positive results. These features allow analysts to be confident and productive knowing the first result is accurate. (PRWeb Aug 22, 2007)\n\n                        Post Comment:Trackback URL: http://www.prweb.com/pingpr.php/WmV0YS1TaW5nLVByb2YtSGFsZi1UaGlyLVplcm8=', 'Promega Plexor(R) HY Most Sensitive Tool for DNA Quantitation', 0, 'In response to DNA analyst''s requests for more sensitive quantitation, Promega announces the release of the Plexor HY System. Plexor HY provides ultra-sensitive quantitation results down to 6.4pg of autosomal or Y-chromosomal DNA. The degree of sensitivity, along with the inclusion of an internal positive control and unique melt curve analysis - guards against false negative and false positive results. These features allow analysts to be confident and productive knowing the first result is accurate. (PRWeb Aug 22, 2007)\n\n                        Post Comment:Trackback URL: http://www.prweb.com/pingpr.php/WmV0YS1TaW5nLVByb2YtSGFsZi1UaGlyLVplcm8=', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'promega-plexorr-hy-most-sensitive-tool-for-dna-quantitation', '', '', '2007-08-23 00:04:00', '2007-08-22 23:04:00', '', 0, 'http://prweb.com/releases/plexor/promega/prweb548634.htm', 0, 'post', '', 0),
