(605, 5, '2007-09-06 14:40:58', '2007-09-06 14:40:58', 'As part of the Kew 2008 programme to improve the public facilities at Kew the public reading rooms will be closed between 1 and 16 December inclusive to allow building work to take place. In addition the readings will also be closed in late January - probably the week of 21 January. The Family Records Centre will, however, remain during both periods.<br />\nFor more information visit <a href="http://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk">http://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk</a> and of course we will cover all the changes in Ancestors.<br />', 'Reading rooms closure - advance warning', 0, 'As part of the Kew 2008 programme to improve the public facilities at Kew the public reading rooms will be closed between 1 and 16 December inclusive to allow building work to take place. In addition the readings will also be closed in late January - probably the week of 21 January. The Family Records Centre will, however, remain during both periods.<br />\nFor more information visit <a href="http://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk">http://www.nationalarchives.gov.uk</a> and of course we will cover all the changes in Ancestors.<br />', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'reading-rooms-closure-advance-warning', '', '', '2007-09-06 14:40:58', '2007-09-06 14:40:58', '', 0, 'http://www.ancestorsmagazine.co.uk/?page=blog#17', 0, 'post', '', 0),
