(658, 8, '2008-12-18 05:00:00', '2008-12-18 05:00:00', '(<i>Florida State University</i>) Sure, they''re polygamous, but male emus and several other ground-dwelling birds also are devoted dads, serving as the sole incubators and caregivers to over-sized broods from multiple mothers. It is rare behavior, but research described in the Dec. 19 Science found that it runs in this avian family, all the way back to its dinosaur ancestors.', 'Polygamy, paternal care in birds linked to dinosaur ancestors', 0, '(<i>Florida State University</i>) Sure, they''re polygamous, but male emus and several other ground-dwelling birds also are devoted dads, serving as the sole incubators and caregivers to over-sized broods from multiple mothers. It is rare behavior, but research described in the Dec. 19 Science found that it runs in this avian family, all the way back to its dinosaur ancestors.', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'polygamy-paternal-care-in-birds-linked-to-dinosaur-ancestors', '', '', '2008-12-18 05:00:00', '2008-12-18 05:00:00', '', 0, 'http://www.eurekalert.org/pub_releases/2008-12/fsu-ppc121808.php', 0, 'post', '', 0),
